677
01:05:13,948 --> 01:05:15,017
Decorum.

678
01:05:15,750 --> 01:05:16,853
Countess.

679
01:05:17,685 --> 01:05:18,953
Sir.

680
01:05:18,953 --> 01:05:20,655
-Welcome...
-Madame Ie Comtesse.

681
01:05:20,655 --> 01:05:26,798
Madame le Comtesse. Seldom, too seldom,
my house receives the presence of nobility.

682
01:05:27,662 --> 01:05:29,971
And, of course, its friends. Please.

683
01:05:31,198 --> 01:05:34,304
Your stay is short. There's not a moment to lose.

684
01:05:34,535 --> 01:05:40,383
My nephew has devised a plan
of metropolitan amusement.

685
01:05:40,875 --> 01:05:45,212
Pleasure is, as you would say, Madame, his forte.

686
01:05:45,212 --> 01:05:46,520
ELIZA: Ah, is it?

687
01:05:49,283 --> 01:05:51,552
Which battle was it, Tom?

688
01:05:51,552 --> 01:05:52,853
ViIIers-en-Cauchies.

689
01:05:52,853 --> 01:05:57,725
Very good.
