690
01:05:57,725 --> 01:06:02,163
Oh. Saving your presence, ma'am.

691
01:06:02,163 --> 01:06:05,333
Be not afraid of abusing
the Jacobins on my account, Judge.

692
01:06:05,333 --> 01:06:09,337
-They guillotined my husband.
-Oh, savages. Beasts.

693
01:06:09,337 --> 01:06:11,544
-And his property?
-Confiscated.

694
01:06:12,306 --> 01:06:13,375
A disaster.

695
01:06:13,874 --> 01:06:17,311
Of course, by then,
much of my wealth was portable, so...

696
01:06:17,311 --> 01:06:18,812
(CHUCKLING)

697
01:06:19,213 --> 01:06:21,749
Yes, portable property
is happiness in a pocketbook.

698
01:06:21,749 --> 01:06:23,558
(LAUGHING)

699
01:06:25,519 --> 01:06:28,022
Do I detect you in irony?

700
01:06:32,326 --> 01:06:37,605
It is my considered opinion
that irony is insult with a smiling face.

701
01:06:38,032 --> 01:06:40,068
HENRY: (LAUGHING) Indeed.

702
01:06:41,202 --> 01:06:42,271
No.

703
01:06:44,405 --> 01:06:45,508
No?

704
01:06:47,008 --> 01:06:51,286
No, irony is the bringing together
of contradictory truths

705
