or I account it as false and a denial
ofthe very nature of humanity itself.

708
01:07:07,862 --> 01:07:09,272
(CHUCKLES)

709
01:07:12,967 --> 01:07:15,470
My cousin is a writer.

710
01:07:17,038 --> 01:07:19,415
-Ofwhat?
-Jane?

711
01:07:22,943 --> 01:07:24,046
Novels.

712
01:07:26,080 --> 01:07:28,617
A young woman offamily?

713
